description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from Vocaloid!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
・Romeo and Cinderella
・Crimson Leaf
・Getting Faster and Faster
・Fixer
・Teo
・Unknown Mother-Goose
・Reverse Universe
・I want to be your heart
・Akari has Arrived
・？？？（Secret）

■Navigator
・KIZUNA AKARI
・MIKU(10th)
・MIKU(Winter)

■Avatar
・HATSUNE MIKU(10th)
・CHIBI LUKA
・CHIBI MIKU

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: VOCALOID Pack 1
